Note: ============================================================================
Note: Single-arg wrapper matching the central dispatcher call shape in
Note: translation.runa: `Return proc hir_to_scala from ScalaEmitter with hir_root`.
Note: Delegates to translate_hir_to_scala which holds the actual translation
Note: pipeline (translator creation, HIR walking, code generation, cleanup).
Note: Introduced in P2-F Round 2B alongside the demolition of the vestigial
Note: scala_emitter.runa shim.
Process called "hir_to_scala" takes hir_root as Integer returns Integer:
    If hir_root is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Return proc translate_hir_to_scala with hir_root
End Process